{
  "name": "RPlog_Surfing_on_Caspar",
  "title": "Riding the Swell at Hideaway Beach",
  "summary": "On the secluded Hideaway Beach below Plaxton City, Orson meets his consort Jessalyn for a surfing lesson on a pair of reworked repulsorboards he has prepared. After a flirtatious exchange of sunscreen and admiring glances, Orson gives her a quick rundown of the board's weight-sensitive controls and leads her out past the channel into the swells. Jessalyn, a Jedi who would have been terrified by such a thing years earlier, takes to it with surprising ease, drawing on the Force to read the waves and ride one cleanly through to the other side. Orson shows off with effortless tricks and a handstand finale, delighting Jessalyn and a small crowd of onlookers gathered on the shore. Exhilarated and happy, the two share their joy in the water before agreeing on a couple more runs and a return to their hotel room.",
